36.ezboard.com/bteamskald.showUserPublicProfile?gid=roseannelottsa>Roseanne Lottsa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Skald TL</span><br>  Posts: 385<br> <font color=#ff0000>(6/18/03 12:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=640.topic>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> RvR experiences of Skalds</span><hr size=1> If you would, please post here a rational description of your experiences playing a Skald in RvR. Please use only real RvR experiences, not BG experiences. I am trying to get a thoughtful thread in one place as opposed to picking through the gazillions of other posts just to find the pieces. <br>
<br>
Remember, real RvR experiences only, not BG. I want both good and bad experiences, so if you have a good experience, post it as well. <br>
<br>
This is not for discussion (Though you can reference this thread in discussions) it's just a place to collect relevant stories) <br>
<br>
